Steps to Debug 
1) Describe a problem.
2) Reproduce the bug .
3) Play computer.
4) Fix the errors .
5) print is your friend.
6) Use debugger .
7) Take a break.
8) Ask a friend (programmer).
9) Run often (run every time when made a slight change in code ).
10) Ask stack overflow.
